data.description: THE BEST OF BOTH WORLDS!  Secluded Craftsman Style Two-Story Home on 5.15 Acres with Ranch Home Attributes. Five (5) Bedrooms, 3.5 Baths, Full Unfinished 1996 sf. Basement. Owner’s Suite, Guest Bedroom, Office and 2.5 Baths on Main. Three (3) Large Bedrooms and 1 Bath Upstairs with Attic Space/Room for Storage. Unfinished Terrace Level is Framed, Wired, Stubbed for a Bath has an HVAC and Garage Door.   Additional Features Include, Freshly Painted Rocking Chair Front Porch, Hardwood Floors and New Carpet on Main Level. Family Room with Built-in Bookcase and Gas Log Fireplace Opens to the Formal Dining Room and has a View of Kitchen with Custom Cabinets, Corian Countertops, Breakfast Bar, Stainless Steel Appliances and Two Pantries.  Owner’s Suite has Jetted Tub, Separate Shower, Double Vanity and Walk-In Closet. Laundry Room/Mud Room is off Garage on Main Level.  Private Wooded Lot, Professionally Landscaped, 220 Breaker on Terrace Level for Hot Tub.  Home is Conveniently Located within Minutes of I-20, Restaurants and Shopping.  Don’t Miss the Opportunity to Make this House your Home!
